trigger_prototypes.expression:
last(/Redfish Nesterkov LLD/redfish.power.voltage.volts[{#VOLTAGE}]) < last(/Redfish Nesterkov LLD/redfish.power.voltage.lower[{#VOLTAGE}])
and
last(/Redfish Nesterkov LLD/redfish.power.voltage.lower[{#VOLTAGE}]) > 0
trigger_prototypes.name: {#VOLTAGE} voltage < LowerThresholdCritical

trigger_prototypes.expression:
last(/Redfish Nesterkov LLD/redfish.power.voltage.volts[{#VOLTAGE}]) > last(/Redfish Nesterkov LLD/redfish.power.voltage.upper[{#VOLTAGE}])
and
last(/Redfish Nesterkov LLD/redfish.power.voltage.upper[{#VOLTAGE}]) > 0
trigger_prototypes.name: {#VOLTAGE} voltage > UpperThresholdCritical

trigger_prototypes.expression:
last(/Redfish Nesterkov LLD/redfish.sensors.status[{#SENSORURL}]) <> "OK"
and
last(/Redfish Nesterkov LLD/redfish.sensors.name[{#SENSORURL}]) <> "ALWAYS_TRUE"
trigger_prototypes.name: Sensor {ITEM.LASTVALUE2} status is {ITEM.LASTVALUE1}

trigger_prototypes.expression: last(/Redfish Nesterkov LLD/redfish.thermal.fan.current[{#FAN}]) < last(/Redfish Nesterkov LLD/redfish.thermal.fan.lower[{#FAN}])
trigger_prototypes.name: {#FAN} speed < LowerThresholdCritical

macros.description: Resource Collection of Sensor instances URL
